Let u\colon Y_\bullet \to X_\bullet be a morphism of topological simplicial spaces, with cone C(u). Let F be an abelian sheaf on X_\bullet and G an abelian sheaf on Y_\bullet , and let f\colon G\to F be a u-morphism. The cone C(f) of f is an abelian sheaf on C(u), and we set
