A mixed Hodge structure H consists of






    a \mathbb {Z}-module H_\mathbb {Z} of finite type (the "integer lattice");





    a finite increasing filtration W of H_\mathbb {Q}=H_\mathbb {Z}\otimes \mathbb {Q} (the "weight filtration");





